sections.heading: Inquest; return to district court; contents; duty
sections.text: The coroner shall return to the district court the inquisition, the papers connected with the same, and a list of the names of witnesses who testified in the matter.SourceLaws 1879, ยง 109, p. 383;R.S.1913, ยง 5676;C.S.1922, ยง 5006;C.S.1929, ยง 26-1515;
